import React from 'react'; import "./Post.css"; import tree from "../../Assets/tree.jpg"; import like from "../../Assets/like.jpg"; import heart from "../../Assets/heart.jpg"; import {MoreVert} from "@material-ui/icons"; import {users} from "../../Components/Dummydata/Dummydata"; export default function Post({post}) { return (
{user = users.filter(u=> u.id===post?.userid)[0].username} {post.date}
{post.desc}
{post.like} people liked it
{post.comment} comments
) }
